==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: guāngyīn sì jiàn

===Etymology===
Literally: Time is like an arrow
===Proverb===
'''[[光陰]][[似]][[箭]]'''
# My how time flys.
===Alternate forms===
